了这个节奏。<br /><br />我喝完酒后：<br /><br />- 人变开朗了<br />- 社交牛逼属性激活了<br />- 人变大方了<br />- 平时让人烦心的小事情变得无关紧要了<br />- 我开始关心其他人了<br />- 我变得更加“善良”了<br />- 生活似乎充满希望了<br /><br />好奇怪啊，多巴胺对脑子的作用这么大的吗。我认为平时的我脑袋是有某种缺陷的，酒精似乎给我一种补全的感觉，真的好奇怪啊人的脑袋，为什么一点酒就会让人的心态发生这么大的变化。<br /><br />我真的很喜欢喝醉的自己，可惜短暂，可惜我会酒醒，那种缺憾感还是会回来。我真的很讨厌清醒的自己。", "last_modified": 1703345209, "replies": 41, "id": 1002931}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 213529, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4060, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 251120, "username": "LxExExl", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/LxExExl", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_mini.png?m=1676792981", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_normal.png?m=1676792981", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_large.png?m=1676792981", "created": 1503883524, "last_modified": 1676792981}, "last_reply_by": "gzhjj", "last_touched": 1703422174, "title": "2023 年 12 月 办理手机卡的正确姿势是什么呢", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002952", "created": 1703382283, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近来国内旅游，没手机号寸步难行。在广州，路边找了一家移动营业厅：\r\n- 8 元月租，感觉很适合收短信验证码，就办了\r\n- 然后客服说要交一个 118 的开户费？交了\r\n- 然后客服选号码，说给我避开 4/7 ，选了一个号码，免费\r\n\r\n\r\n然后举牌拍照，过程丝滑。\r\n\r\n我好奇是我没做功课吗？我记得 10 年前淘宝买号码，寄到家里激活拍照，没 118 这种激活费？\r\n\r\n\r\n还要给老婆办一个，来 v 站问问。正确的开户姿势是怎样呢？谢谢🙏。", "content_rendered": "<p>最近来国内旅游，没手机号寸步难行。在广州，路边找了一家移动营业厅：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>8 元月租，感觉很适合收短信验证码，就办了</li>\n<li>然后客服说要交一个 118 的开户费？交了</li>\n<li>然后客服选号码，说给我避开 4/7 ，选了一个号码，免费</li>\n</ul>\n<p>然后举牌拍照，过程丝滑。</p>\n<p>我好奇是我没做功课吗？我记得 10 年前淘宝买号码，寄到家里激活拍照，没 118 这种激活费？</p>\n<p>还要给老婆办一个，来 v 站问问。正确的开户姿势是怎样呢？谢谢🙏。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1703382283, "replies": 32, "id": 1002952}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fccb/3cdc/680_large.png?m=1583581439", "name": "paypal", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fccb/3cdc/680_normal.png?m=1583581439", "title": "PayPal", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/paypal", "topics": 199, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "PayPal", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fccb/3cdc/680_mini.png?m=1583581439", "stars": 163, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 680, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 73605, "username": "mitoop", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mitoop", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_mini.png?m=1703390287", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_normal.png?m=1703390287", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_large.png?m=1703390287", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_xlarge.png?m=1703390287", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_xlarge.png?m=1703390287", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2757/9f80/73605_xlarge.png?m=1703390287", "created": 1410447290, "last_modified": 1703390287}, "last_reply_by": "Hider5", "last_touched": 1703423035, "title": "paypal 有 100 刀, 提取到银行卡太麻烦, 可以干点啥", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1002970", "created": 1703390299, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1703395448, "replies": 31, "id": 1002970}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", 